title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 05.09.08
description:
MONSTER MOM:

Sandy&#039;s son was determined to be a victim of shaken baby syndrome he has severe head damage and Sandy is accused of abusing her 3 month old infant. She says that while her husband was at work she had left her son with her parents while she could go get high. upon "discovering" that her her son had been abused she blamed a 3-year old and a dog that she said was viscous.
